but I can't remember.

50:51.004 --> 50:52.701
I can't...

50:52.745 --> 50:56.096
Have you tried dating
or seeing someone else?

50:56.140 --> 50:58.620
No. No.

50:58.664 --> 51:01.536
Though I got involved
with Nadine.

51:01.580 --> 51:02.972
Which...

51:03.016 --> 51:06.541
- That was stupid.
- Nadine, Nadine, Nadine.

51:06.585 --> 51:08.891
It got me fired, and now
I have a meeting with Bob.

51:08.935 --> 51:11.111
Who's Bob?

51:11.155 --> 51:12.895
Nadine's husband.

51:12.939 --> 51:15.898
Why are you meeting
with her husband?

51:15.942 --> 51:18.249
He wants to get coffee
at 3:00.

51:18.292 --> 51:20.425
Scratch that, 3:30.

51:20.468 --> 51:23.384
And I have to go to
my daughter's Career Day.

51:23.428 --> 51:26.822
I have to speak at my daughter's
Career Day. What am I gonna say?

51:26.866 --> 51:30.130
I would not mention
the coffeemaker

51:30.174 --> 51:32.524
or getting fired

51:32.567 --> 51:34.003
or Nadine.

51:35.396 --> 51:37.529
Well, Daniel,
I'd love to talk all day,

51:37.572 --> 51:40.271
but I do still
work here, so...

51:40.314 --> 51:43.317
This does mark the end of your
tenure here at Field Publishing,

51:43.361 --> 51:46.973
but I just want you to know
that I am available to you.

51:47.016 --> 51:49.062
Okay? If you're
ever in distress,

51:49.106 --> 51:51.673
need support,
or just a friendly voice,

51:51.717 --> 51:54.111
I'm just a phone call away,
okay?

51:54.154 --> 51:57.766
I may not be a registered therapist,
but I am a registered friend.

51:58.941 --> 52:01.205
Thank you.

52:01.248 --> 52:03.772
All right, good luck
out there, okay?

52:03.816 --> 52:05.470
- Yeah.
- Gonna need it.

52:05.513 --> 52:08.429
Oh, hey, Daniel?
I should mention to you

52:08.473 --> 52:11.258
that Mr. Schneedy
requested that we cite

52:11.302 --> 52:13.608
improper conduct as the reason
for your termination,

52:13.652 --> 52:16.524
so you won't get unemployment
in this state.

52:16.568 --> 52:19.266
- Serious?
- I know.

52:19.310 --> 52:21.442
It's like, my hands
are so tied, you know,

52:21.486 --> 52:23.314
but I think part
of being human--

52:23.357 --> 52:25.142
You're an asshole.

52:26.534 --> 52:28.057
Beth!

52:30.712 --> 52:33.062
See him out!

52:33.106 --> 52:35.239
Uh, let's see. Where
did we leave off last time?

52:35.282 --> 52:38.024
We were talking
about the mayor.

52:38.067 --> 52:40.592
Does anybody remember
where we left-- Patricia?

52:40.635 --> 52:42.768
Um, Darius is gone.

52:42.811 --> 52:45.074
- What?
- Darius, the new kid?

52:46.163 --> 52:47.860
Oh. No, he was here.

52:47.903 --> 52:49.644
Um, but he's not now.

52:49.688 --> 52:51.907
Well, you know what?
He probably got lost.

52:51.951 --> 52:53.953
If he's not back in five
minutes, I'll go look for him.

52:53.996 --> 52:55.476
Okay.

52:55.520 --> 52:57.478
We were on 108.
Page 108.

